name: Sande (Zogbe) Spirits
shortLoreBlurb: Sande (Zogbe) Spirits is a spirits/class from Sierra Leone/Liberia associated with women’s society, water. Appeased for safe passage and rains.
overlapsLinks: Manannán (Celtic), Naga (India/SE Asia), Poseidon (Greek), Tangaroa (Polynesia), Yemaya (Yoruba)
